characterDescription:
Ty is a Skybreaker squire under the tutelage of Master Warren.
He is the leader of a group of other such squires who trail Szeth in one of their training operations.
Batting pouches of colored dust away from himself, Szeth directs them toward Ty, which won't count as marks, but the dust gets in Ty's eyes, causing him to blink and slow.
When Ty calls to the others, pointing up at Szeth, he tells them to get him.
